Output docs/media/hero.gif

Require bash

Set Shell "bash"
Set Width 1280
Set Height 720
Set FontSize 26
Set FontFamily "Menlo"
Set LetterSpacing 0
Set Theme "TokyoNight"
Set Padding 32
Set Framerate 30
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set MarginFill "#070b16"
Set Margin 12
Set BorderRadius 18
Set WindowBar "ColorfulRight"
Set WindowBarSize 36
Set TypingSpeed 12ms

Hide
Type "clear && bash docs/demo/hero.sh"
Enter
Show
Sleep 22s
